{"tid":2204592,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"灣仔831暴動案　辯方質疑警長拾警棍放入被告背囊","createTime":"2020-09-16T07:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:30:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":140,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c2baec1cfd293d7c7e2a8218fe06af7525ee1194","tid":2204592,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社工陳虹秀等8人被控去年8月31日在灣仔參與暴動，區域法院續審。辯方質疑作供警長在地上拾起一枝伸縮警棍，之後放入被告的背囊內。<br />\n<br />\n控方傳召當日有份制服第四被告龔梓舜的速龍小隊成員警長黃子誠作供。他稱，當日在修頓球場外驅散人群時，撲倒第四被告並拿走他的背囊；事後他在背囊中發現伸縮警棍及疑似汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n辯方播放案發片段，質疑警長最初只是手持背囊，但之後他曾踎低拾起物件，手上隨即多了一枝棍狀物體；警長否認是踎低拾起物件，一度稱片中所見的棍狀物體是手指，之後改稱是頭盔帶，及後又稱是他腰間的警棍移位。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑，片段中明顯見他用右手手持警棍，警長再回應稱「不肯定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405770&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTve6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=668fede1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405770&h=62fdf88d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405770</a>"},{"pid":"6ceb0a8b68a77a0ac16a08d883390359a88fb8ef","tid":2204592,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b06bf45bf2f33f7c6476c78773111887394f71b","tid":2204592,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill